picButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528743\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528743\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iwm1665703132785.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iwm1665703132785.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iwm1665703132785.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iwm1665703132785\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__ugetname_403432\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of the Windows object associated with a window handle.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__topic_d120356e1_d120357e1_d120358e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104iwm1665703132785_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__codeblock_jf5_3zz_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;windows.h&gt;\n\nunsigned char* ugetname (HWNDhWnd,unsigned char*name,intlen);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__topic_d85597e1_d85598e1_d85599e1_d85600e1_d85601e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d701270e58\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__parml_iws_jzz_zvb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hWnd</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Window handle of a Microsoft Windows object within the calling Uniface\n                  application.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">name</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">String that receives the name of the Windows object.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">len</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Maximum number of characters to be placed in the buffer pointed to by\n                     <var class=\"keyword varname\">name</var>. Because this does not include the zero terminator, the\n                  buffer should be defined one byte larger than the value of\n                  <var class=\"keyword varname\">len</var>.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__topic_d85602e1_d85603e1_d85604e1_d85605e1_d85606e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d701270e103\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14864e1_d14865e1_d14866e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by ugetname</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14864e1_d14865e1_d14866e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14864e1_d14865e1_d14866e1__entry__2\">Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14864e1_d14865e1_d14866e1__entry__1\">0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14864e1_d14865e1_d14866e1__entry__2\">The specified window handle is not recognized\n                        by Uniface. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14864e1_d14865e1_d14866e1__entry__1\">&lt;&gt;0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14864e1_d14865e1_d14866e1__entry__2\">\n A pointer to the name of the window. This value is the memory address of the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var> parameter.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__p_d120371e1_d120372e1_d120373e1\">The exact contents of the string returned in\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">name</var> depend on the type of object indicated by\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">hWnd</var>. The possibilities are described in the following table.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Object names returned by ugetname</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Object Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\">Name Returned </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\"> 4GL debug</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UDEBUG&gt;ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Application</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Entity scroll bar</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UTDB.EntityName.\n                           ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Field</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\n                           FieldName.EntityName.ModelName.FormName. ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Form</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">FormName.ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Form canvas</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">FormName.\n                        ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Form panel</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">PanelName.FormName.\n                           ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Form panel button</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\n                           ButtonText.PanelName.FormName.ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Message frame</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UFRAME.ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Message line</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UniCombo.ULINE.ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Pop-up panel</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">PanelName.FormName.ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Session panel</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">PanelName.ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Session panel button</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ButtonText.PanelName.ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Toolbar</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UTOOLBAR.\n                        ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__1\">Toolbar button</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iwm1665703132785__table_d14867e1_d14868e1_d14869e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ButtonText.UTOOLBAR.\n                           ApplicationName</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__note_N10225_N1006B_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If an application or form has a\n            specific title, that title will be returned instead of the name. So,\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">ApplicationName</var> can also mean <var class=\"keyword varname\">ApplicationTitle</var>.\n            The name returned for form panel buttons is language-dependent, that is, it corresponds\n            to the Button Text information from the language setup, which can contain embedded\n            spaces.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__topic_d85607e1_d85608e1_d85609e1_d85610e1_d85611e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d701270e356\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__d6421e20\">Microsoft Windows platforms only. In library\n          <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__topic_d85612e1_d85613e1_d85614e1_d85615e1_d85616e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d701270e369\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__p_d120383e1_d120384e1_d120385e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ugetname</code> returns the name of the\n            Microsoft Windows object associated with the given window handle. You can get\n            information only about Microsoft Windows objects that are part of the calling Uniface\n            application. Note that the length of the supplied buffer must be one byte greater that\n            the value specified by the <var class=\"keyword varname\">len</var> parameter.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__p_d120386e1_d120387e1_d120388e1\">The type <code class=\"ph codeph\">HWND</code> is defined in the\n            include file <span class=\"ph filepath\">windows.h</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__section_gyx_hd1_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d701270e392\">Example: ugetname and ugethwnd</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugethwnd</code> and\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugetname</code> to obtain the Uniface application window handle and title.\n            It then changes the application title a couple of times (implementing a simple progress\n            indicator) and finally restores it back to its original value.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104iwm1665703132785_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"iwm1665703132785__codeblock_tyj_jd1_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n#include &lt;windows.h&gt;\n\nEXPORT void PHASECOUNTER ()\n{\nHWND hApp;\nchar name[201];\nchar txt[50];\nint i;\n\nhApp = ugethwnd(); /* Get application window handle */\nugetname(hApp, name, sizeof(name)-1); /* Get window title */\n\nfor ( i=1; i&lt;10; i++ ) /* During 10 seconds ... */\n{\nsprintf(txt, \"Phase %d of 10\", i);\nSetWindowText(hApp, txt); /* Change application window title */\nSleep(1000); /* Pause 1 second */\n}\n\nSetWindowText(hApp, name); /* Restore application window title*/\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528743\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528743\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ugetname Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the name of the Windows object associated with a window handle. Explain this code #include <windows.h> unsigned char* ugetname (HWNDhWnd,unsigned char*name,intlen); Copy Parameters hWnd Window handle of a Microsoft Windows object within the calling Uniface application. name String that receives the name of the Windows object. len Maximum number of characters to be placed in the buffer pointed to by name . Because this does not include the zero terminator, the buffer should be defined one byte larger than the value of len . Return Values Table 1. Values returned by ugetname Value Meaning 0 The specified window handle is not recognized by Uniface. <>0 A pointer to the name of the window. This value is the memory address of the Name parameter. The exact contents of the string returned in name depend on the type of object indicated by hWnd . The possibilities are described in the following table. Table 2. Object names returned by ugetname Object Type Name Returned 4GL debug UDEBUG>ApplicationName Application ApplicationName Entity scroll bar UTDB.EntityName. ApplicationName Field FieldName.EntityName.ModelName.FormName. ApplicationName Form FormName.ApplicationName Form canvas FormName. ApplicationName Form panel PanelName.FormName. ApplicationName Form panel button ButtonText.PanelName.FormName.ApplicationName Message frame UFRAME.ApplicationName Message line UniCombo.ULINE.ApplicationName Pop-up panel PanelName.FormName.ApplicationName Session panel PanelName.ApplicationName Session panel button ButtonText.PanelName.ApplicationName Toolbar UTOOLBAR. ApplicationName Toolbar button ButtonText.UTOOLBAR. ApplicationName Note: If an application or form has a specific title, that title will be returned instead of the name. So, ApplicationName can also mean ApplicationTitle . The name returned for form panel buttons is language-dependent, that is, it corresponds to the Button Text information from the language setup, which can contain embedded spaces. Use Microsoft Windows platforms only. In library yrtl . Description ugetname returns the name of the Microsoft Windows object associated with the given window handle. You can get information only about Microsoft Windows objects that are part of the calling Uniface application. Note that the length of the supplied buffer must be one byte greater that the value specified by the len parameter. The type HWND is defined in the include file windows.h . Example: ugetname and ugethwnd The following example uses ugethwnd and ugetname to obtain the Uniface application window handle and title. It then changes the application title a couple of times (implementing a simple progress indicator) and finally restores it back to its original value. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> #include <windows.h> EXPORT void PHASECOUNTER () { HWND hApp; char name[201]; char txt[50]; int i; hApp = ugethwnd(); /* Get application window handle */ ugetname(hApp, name, sizeof(name)-1); /* Get window title */ for ( i=1; i<10; i++ ) /* During 10 seconds ... */ { sprintf(txt, \"Phase %d of 10\", i); SetWindowText(hApp, txt); /* Change application window title */ Sleep(1000); /* Pause 1 second */ } SetWindowText(hApp, name); /* Restore application window title*/ } Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}